      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FROM A DISTANCE (1) is a talented dog who has been too quick to win his last two on end, the latest leading throughout at Q Straight (19.08). Has a good record here including 11 wins. Ideally placed to take this out. ZIPPING URBAN (7) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with three wins and a placing from five tries. Missed the frame latest (29.84) when fourth over 510m at Rockhampton in a OPEN. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. NO MORE BEER (2) has a terrific record this track and trip with six wins and four placings from 10 starts. Scored by 2.25 lengths last time (18.87) in a Grade 4/5 over 350m at Q Straight. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. HARA'S ODEN (5) placed last time (25.54) at this track in a OPEN, finishing third and beaten 2 lengths. Has three wins already from this draw.",
